This project show how to run the phamtomJs script on GAE.

1. Create the project in google cloud.
2. Create the ubuntu instance.
3. Connect to the instance with ssh terminal.
4. Do the following command.
    - sudo apt-get update
    - sudo apt-get install git-core
    - sudo apt-get install python-pip python-dev build-essential
    - sudo apt-get install libfontconfig
5. Clone the demo project and run the script.
    - git clone https://github.com/yingtaiGithub/phamtomjs_demo/
    - go into the project directory and then run the script; python scrapers.py

    Note: The demo project go to the 'http://formyip.com' and take the screenshot of the page 'check.png'.
6. Check whether the script works well with 'check.png'.
